The previous mayor
Kameyama-san, Kawashima-san,

98
00:06:00.971 --> 00:06:04.911
the current mayor Kuroiwa, and Nishimoto-san.

99
00:06:04.911 --> 00:06:05.281
What?

100
00:06:05.791 --> 00:06:08.791
