daughter just the other day.

104
00:06:19.471 --> 00:06:23.031
Really? What about the mayor's
secretary Hirata-san?

105
00:06:23.031 --> 00:06:25.411
He's a strange fellow.

106
00:06:25.411 --> 00:06:27.511
I don't know what he was doing,

107
00:06:27.671 --> 00:06:31.521
but I often saw him secretly meeting with
Kawashima-san at the community center.

108
00:06:31.671 --> 00:06:33.761
What about Shimizu-san?

109
00:06:33.761 --> 00:06:35.761
He's a respectable man.

110
00:06:35.761 --> 00:06:38.901
