223
00:12:35.068 --> 00:12:36.848
Could I go buy something to drink?

224
00:12:37.318 --> 00:12:39.178
I'm thirsty.

225
00:12:39.598 --> 00:12:41.038
Very well.

226
00:12:45.938 --> 00:12:47.218
Hey, mister.

227
00:12:47.698 --> 00:12:49.698
