231
00:13:01.708 --> 00:13:03.418
K-Kid!

232
00:13:05.518 --> 00:13:09.398
I finally found the sheet
music Aso-san left behind.

233
00:13:09.398 --> 00:13:10.448
Let me see that.

234
00:13:10.448 --> 00:13:11.588
Hey.

235
00:13:12.668 --> 00:13:15.398
"To my son Seiji."

236
00:13:16.928 --> 00:13:22.058
I thought Aso-san had a wife and
daughter who he took with him.

237
00:13:23.078 --> 00:13:25.438
Come to think of it, he had a son, too.

238
00:13:25.678 --> 00:13:31.148
He fell terribly ill as a child and
was hospitalized on the mainland.

239
00:13:31.148 --> 00:13:33.188
I believe his name was...

240
00:13:33.188 --> 00:13:34.418
Seiji.

241
00:13:35.918 --> 00:13:36.698
Could it be?

242
00:13:46.788 --> 00:13:49.128
I see. So that's how it is.

243
00:13:49.388 --> 00:13:54.808
The reason the culprit moved Kawashima-san
to the piano room after drowning him.

244
00:13:55.798 --> 00:13:58.848
