left at all three crime scenes.

245
00:14:00.168 --> 00:14:03.638
And the mystery of the code written in blood.

246
00:14:04.408 --> 00:14:07.658
It's definitely them. They're the culprit.

247
00:14:09.148 --> 00:14:11.148
