begin playing the B side.

293
00:16:41.778 --> 00:16:45.868
But the auto-reverse feature inverts the
tape head to play the opposite side.

294
00:16:46.658 --> 00:16:48.508
Take a look at the crime scene photos.

295
00:16:49.258 --> 00:16:53.638
There's a switch shining next to the body's neck,

296
00:16:53.638 --> 00:16:57.848
but in the photo taken after
the body was moved, it's gone.

297
00:16:58.638 --> 00:17:03.378
